{"tid":590605,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主國家]瑞士將再舉行公民投票 決定是否買新戰機","createTime":"2018-03-12T19:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T01:50:53.000Z","uid":132859,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9e74982931c68c018d3bdc2087483d2b1a0cbc64","tid":590605,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T19:09:28.000Z","msg":"瑞士聯邦委員會9日宣布，將再度提出公民投票，讓全民決定是否要採購新一代噴射戰鬥機。<br />\n<br />\n　去年11月聯邦委員會決定，花費84億美元（約新臺幣2456.8億元）採購新戰機與飛彈防禦系統，這也是瑞士史上最大筆的軍事採購案。由於採購新戰機涉及大筆公共支出，並且影響國家安全重大，因此瑞士再度將此議題付諸公投，其最晚會在2020年舉行投票，以尋求在2025年交機、2030年具完整戰力；至於採購戰機型號則會在投票後決定。<br />\n<br />\n　瑞士過去已兩度公投表決採購新戰機─其包括1993年決定採購美製F/A-18戰機與2014年否決採購瑞典紳寶公司獅鷲戰機。<br />\n<br />\n　不過和平團體批評瑞士政府的做法「極不民主」，強調瑞士不先公布計畫採購機型，讓選民無從得知採購戰機的成本、數量與可進行任務，因此將「反對到底」。<br />\n<br />\n　瑞士空軍現有31架F/A-18C/D戰機，以及53架F-5E/F，兩者都已逐漸老舊，因此瑞士在2014年公投決定是否以22架「獅鷲」汰換，但53.8%選民反對。為了讓F/A-18C/D戰機能夠持續使用到新戰機服役，瑞士政府已編列預算，升級延壽F/A-18機隊。<br />\n<br />\n　目前瑞士可能採購選項包括F-35、F/A-18E/F超級大黃蜂、歐洲颱風戰機、法國飆風戰機與瑞典「獅鷲」最新版本JAS-39E。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/280845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F280845&d=LOaIFZsR68d32QMx6awQTcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=b6400023\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/280845</a><br />\n平過高鐵都要公投<br />\n鬼佬做野邊似我哋咁有中囯速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3161400b4c2d1a04db37b841242691eadf193106","tid":590605,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.commisceo-global.com/images/easyblog_images/63/problem-solving-cultural-differences.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commisceo-global.com%2Fimages%2Feasyblog_images%2F63%2Fproblem-solving-cultural-differences.jpg&h=3729dbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6851a3b3cebd6053036fb741017a11c27d5458d7","tid":590605,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3161400b4c2d1a04db37b841242691eadf193106","tid":590605,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T00:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.commisceo-global.com/images/easyblog_images/63/problem-solving-cultural-differences.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commisceo-global.com%2Fimages%2Feasyblog_images%2F63%2Fproblem-solving-cultural-differences.jpg&h=3729dbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"其實瑞典冇咁差ge"}]}